reviewText:
after watching the first 20 minutes of this dvd i hate to say but the dvd was not what i suspected, very poor.
what else can i say,

The Video is of a on the side wrestling event that plays to every guy out there and throws in a tit here and a flash there.  The Wrestling is scripted and very soft core.  These women are just there to show off.  Some are actually good and one in particular just used her weight to win the matches no matter the cost.  But fortunately she looses in the final match but not before gouging her opponent and leaving some massive teeth marks and nail scratches on the winner.  It is a bit worse than some of the other wrestling videos out there but to each their own.
